# 子查询
  查询（query）任何SQL语句都是查询。
  SQL允许创建子查询（subquery）
# 利用子查询进行过滤
  可以把一条SELECT语句返回的结果用于另一条SELECT语句的WHERE子句。
  
  SELECT order_name 
  FROM orderitems
  WHERE prod_id = 'TNT2';
                                      => SELECT cust_id
  SELECT cust_id                         FROM orders
  FROM orders                            WHERE order_num IN (SELECT order_num
  WHERE order_num IN (20005, 20007);                         FROM orderitems
                                                             WHERE prod_id = 'TNT2');
  
  格式化SQL
    分解为多行，进行适当缩进
      SELECT cust_name, cust_contact
      FROM customers
      WHERE cust_id IN (SELECT cust_id
                        FROM orders
                        WHERE order_num IN (SELECT order_num
                                            FROM orderitems
                                            WHERE prod_id = 'TNT'));
                                            
  列必须相同

# 作为计算字段使用子查询
      SELECT cust_name,
             cust_state,
             (SELECT COUNT(*)
              FROM orders
              WHERE orders.cust_id = custorms.cust_id) AS orders
      FROM customers
      ORDER BY cust_name;
      
  相关子查询（correlated subquery）涉及外部查询的子查询
